This dashboard uses the `.monitoring-es-8-*` index pattern to provide an overview of cluster metrics for Elasticsearch 8.x.

The underlying metrics on this dashboard are only collected every 10 seconds (by default). This means that collections are only a point in time/snapshot of what was happening when the call was made to the Node Stats API, so please use this dashboard as an indicator of cluster activity in conjunction with the Cluster logs, Proxy logs, and Docker metrics.

attributes.description:
Number of indexing/write/bulk requests queued, per node. 

This gauge is only collected once per minute (a point in time snapshot), and so a sudden burst in requests may not be captured on this graph, which is why you may see rejected requests - but the queue, and active thread counts look 'low'.

NOTE: There are changes between 5.x, 6.x, 7.x and the indexing/write/bulk request thread pools (hence the three underlying queries).
attributes.title: Indexing Thread Pool Queue

attributes.description: Number of indexing/write requests rejected, per node over a 60s window. If the bucket size is >60s, then this is an average number of rejected request per minute over that bucket.
attributes.title: Indexing Rejections

attributes.description: Query request rate, per node.
attributes.title: Query Request Rate

attributes.description:
The average service time for queries on a node, taken by dividing the total time spent servicing queries by the total count.

Exclusive of any client side queuing or network hops between the proxy.
attributes.title: Average Query Service Time (ms)

attributes.description:
Number of search requests queued, per node.

This gauge is only collected once per minute (a point in time snapshot), and so a sudden burst in requests may not be captured on this graph, which is why you may see rejected requests - but the queue, and active thread counts look 'low'.
attributes.title: Search Thread Pool Queue

attributes.description: Number of search requests rejected, per node.
attributes.title: Search Rejections

attributes.description: The total number of operations in the Translog for all indices on a node, at collection time (once every 60s).
attributes.title: All Indices Translog Operations

attributes.description: Shows the number of docs deleted per node, within a 60s bucket. If the bucket is greater than 60s, then it is the average number of deleted documents per 60s for that window.
attributes.title: Deleted Docs

attributes.description:
An emulated 'Stack Monitoring' dashboard, using metrics from the .monitoring-es-8-* index pattern. 

Use this dashboard to get an overview of a particular cluster's performance, similar to the metrics customer's see in their Monitoring Clusters.

  "$schema": "https://vega.github.io/schema/vega/v5.2.json",
  "data": [
    {
      "name": "rawData",
      "url": {
        "%context%": true,
        "%timefield%": "@timestamp",
        "index": "consumption-*",
        "body": {
          "aggs": {
            "dimensions": {
              "multi_terms": {
                "terms": [
                  {"field": "deployment_name"},
                  {"field": "category"},
                  {"field": "sku"}
                ],
                "size": 10000
              },
              "aggs": {"cost": {"sum": {"field": "cost"}}}
            }
          },
          "size": 0
        }
      },
      "format": {"property": "aggregations.dimensions.buckets"},
      "transform": [
        {"type": "formula", "expr": "datum.key[0]", "as": "stk1"},
        {"type": "formula", "expr": "datum.key[1]", "as": "stk2"},
        {"type": "formula", "expr": "datum.key[2]", "as": "stk3"},
        {"type": "formula", "expr": "datum.cost.value", "as": "size"},
        {"type": "filter", "expr": "datum.size != 0"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "nodes",
      "source": "rawData",
      "transform": [
        {
          "type": "formula",
          "expr": "datum.stk1+'|'+datum.stk2+'|'+datum.stk3",
          "as": "key"
        },
        {
          "type": "fold",
          "fields": ["stk1", "stk2", "stk3"],
          "as": ["stack", "grpId"]
        },
        {
          "type": "formula",
          "expr": "datum.stack == 'stk1' ? datum.stk1 : (datum.stack == 'stk2' ? datum.stk2 : datum.stk3)",
          "as": "sortField"
        },
        {
          "type": "stack",
          "groupby": ["stack"],
          "sort": {"field": "sortField", "order": "descending"},
          "field": "size"
        },
        {"type": "formula", "expr": "(datum.y0+datum.y1)/2", "as": "yc"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "groups",
      "source": "nodes",
      "transform": [
        {
          "type": "aggregate",
          "groupby": ["stack", "grpId"],
          "fields": ["size"],
          "ops": ["sum"],
          "as": ["total"]
        },
        {
          "type": "stack",
          "groupby": ["stack"],
          "sort": {"field": "grpId", "order": "descending"},
          "field": "total"
        },
        {"type": "formula", "expr": "scale('y', datum.y0)", "as": "scaledY0"},
        {"type": "formula", "expr": "scale('y', datum.y1)", "as": "scaledY1"},
        {
          "type": "formula",
          "expr": "datum.stack == 'stk1'",
          "as": "rightLabel"
        },
        {
          "type": "formula",
          "expr": "datum.total/domain('y')[1]",
          "as": "percentage"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "leftNodes",
      "source": "groups",
      "transform": [{"type": "filter", "expr": "datum.stack == 'stk1'"}]
    },
    {
      "name": "middleNodes",
      "source": "nodes",
      "transform": [{"type": "filter", "expr": "datum.stack == 'stk2'"}]
    },
    {
      "name": "destinationNodes",
      "source": "nodes",
      "transform": [{"type": "filter", "expr": "datum.stack == 'stk3'"}]
    },
    {
      "name": "middleEdges",
      "source": "nodes",
      "transform": [
        {"type": "filter", "expr": "datum.stack == 'stk1'"},
        {
          "type": "lookup",
          "from": "middleNodes",
          "key": "key",
          "fields": ["key"],
          "values": ["y0", "y1", "yc"],
          "as": ["target_y0", "target_y1", "target_yc"]
        },
        {
          "type": "linkpath",
          "orient": "horizontal",
          "shape": "diagonal",
          "sourceY": {"expr": "scale('y', datum.yc)"},
          "sourceX": {"expr": "scale('x', 'stk1') + bandwidth('x')"},
          "targetY": {"expr": "scale('y', datum.target_yc)"},
          "targetX": {"expr": "scale('x', 'stk2')"}
        },
        {
          "type": "formula",
          "expr": "range('y')[0]-scale('y', datum.size)",
          "as": "strokeWidth"
        },
        {
          "type": "formula",
          "expr": "datum.size/domain('y')[1]",
          "as": "percentage"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "rightEdges",
      "source": "nodes",
      "transform": [
        {"type": "filter", "expr": "datum.stack == 'stk2'"},
        {
          "type": "lookup",
          "from": "destinationNodes",
          "key": "key",
          "fields": ["key"],
          "as": ["target"]
        },
        {
          "type": "linkpath",
          "orient": "horizontal",
          "shape": "diagonal",
          "sourceY": {"expr": "scale('y', datum.yc)"},
          "sourceX": {"expr": "scale('x', 'stk2') + bandwidth('x')"},
          "targetY": {"expr": "scale('y', datum.target.yc)"},
          "targetX": {"expr": "scale('x', 'stk3')"}
        },
        {
          "type": "formula",
          "expr": "range('y')[0]-scale('y', datum.size)",
          "as": "strokeWidth"
        },
        {
          "type": "formula",
          "expr": "datum.size/domain('y')[1]",
          "as": "percentage"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "scales": [
    {
      "name": "x",
      "type": "band",
      "range": "width",
      "domain": ["stk1", "stk2", "stk3"],
      "paddingOuter": 0.05,
      "paddingInner": 0.95
    },
    {
      "name": "y",
      "type": "linear",
      "range": "height",
      "domain": {"data": "nodes", "field": "y1"}
    },
    {

  "axes": [

        }
      }
    },
    {"orient": "left", "scale": "y"}
  ],
  "marks": [
    {
      "type": "path",
      "name": "middleEdgesMark",
      "from": {"data": "middleEdges"},
      "clip": true,
      "encode": {
        "update": {
          "stroke": [
            {"scale": "color", "field": "stk1"}
          ],
          "strokeWidth": {"field": "strokeWidth"},

            "signal": "(groupHover.stk1 == datum.stk1 || groupHover.stk2 == datum.stk2 || (edgeHover.stk1 == datum.stk1 && edgeHover.stk2 == datum.stk2 && edgeHover.stk3 == datum.stk3)) ? 0.9 : 0.3"
          },
          "zindex": {
            "signal": "(groupHover.stk1 == datum.stk1 || groupHover.stk2 == datum.stk2 || (edgeHover.stk1 == datum.stk1 && edgeHover.stk2 == datum.stk2 && edgeHover.stk3 == datum.stk3)) ? 1 : 0"
          },
          "tooltip": {
            "signal": "{title: datum.stk1 + ' → ' + datum.stk2 + ' → ' + datum.stk3, price: format(datum.size, ',.2f') + ' ECU', percent: format(datum.percentage, '.1%')}"
          }
        },
        "hover": {"strokeOpacity": {"value": 1}}
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "path",
      "name": "rightEdgesMark",
      "from": {"data": "rightEdges"},
      "clip": true,
      "encode": {
        "update": {
          "stroke": [
            {"scale": "color", "field": "stk3"}
          ],
          "strokeWidth": {"field": "strokeWidth"},
          "path": {"field": "path"},
          "strokeOpacity": {
            "signal": "(groupHover.stk2 == datum.stk2 || groupHover.stk3 == datum.stk3 || (edgeHover.stk1 == datum.stk1 && edgeHover.stk2 == datum.stk2 && edgeHover.stk3 == datum.stk3)) ? 0.9 : 0.3"
          },
          "zindex": {
            "signal": "(groupHover.stk2 == datum.stk2 || groupHover.stk3 == datum.stk3 || (edgeHover.stk1 == datum.stk1 && edgeHover.stk2 == datum.stk2 && edgeHover.stk3 == datum.stk3)) ? 1 : 0"
          },
          "tooltip": {
            "signal": "{title: datum.stk1 + ' → ' + datum.stk2 + ' → ' + datum.stk3, price: format(datum.size, ',.2f') + ' ECU', percent: format(datum.percentage, '.1%')}"
          }
        },
        "hover": {"strokeOpacity": {"value": 1}}
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "rect",
      "name": "groupMark",
      "from": {"data": "groups"},
      "encode": {
        "enter": {
          "fill": {"scale": "color", "field": "grpId"},
          "width": {"scale": "x", "band": 1}
        },
        "update": {
          "x": {"scale": "x", "field": "stack"},
          "y": {"field": "scaledY0"},
          "y2": {"field": "scaledY1"},
          "fillOpacity": {"value": 0.6},
          "tooltip": {
            "signal": "{title: datum.grpId, price: format(datum.total, ',.2f') + ' ECU', percent: format(datum.percentage, '.1%')}"
          }
        },
        "hover": {"fillOpacity": {"value": 1}}
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "from": {"data": "groups"},
      "interactive": false,
      "encode": {
        "update": {
          "x": {
            "signal": "scale('x', datum.stack) + (datum.rightLabel ? bandwidth('x') + 8 : -8)"
          },
          "yc": {"signal": "(datum.scaledY0 + datum.scaledY1)/2"},
          "align": {"signal": "datum.rightLabel ? 'left' : 'right'"},
          "baseline": {"value": "middle"},
          "fontWeight": {
            "signal": "groupHover[datum.stack] == datum.grpId || edgeHover[datum.stack] == datum.grpId ? 'bold' : 'normal'"
          },
          "text": {
            "signal": "abs(datum.scaledY0-datum.scaledY1) > 13 ? datum.grpId : ''"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "rect",
      "from": {"data": "groups"},
      "encode": {
        "enter": {
          "stroke": {"value": "#000"},
          "strokeWidth": {"value": 2},
          "width": {"scale": "x", "band": 1},
          "x": {"scale": "x", "field": "stack"},
          "y": {"field": "y0", "scale": "y"},
          "y2": {"field": "y1", "scale": "y"}
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "signals": [
    {
      "name": "groupHover",

      ]
    }

**This dashboard requires that "Collect Agent Metrics" are configured on the relevant Elastic Agent policy.**

**This dashboard requires that "Collect Agent Metrics" are configured on the relevant Elastic Agent policy.**

Use the Metric counters to Drilldown to the specific Input Dashboard.**  

**This dashboard requires that "Collect Agent Metrics" are configured on the relevant Elastic Agent policy.**
